metadata.name: Ode To Sartoshi - Birth
metadata.description:
As a thank you to Sartoshi’s vision and creativity, I created my first digital piece and first minted piece for that fibonacci forward thinking mfer.  This piece is similar to what Sartoshi received, all pieces in this collection are hand drawn individual pieces.  Each, including the first sent to Sartoshi, has its own unique Ode To Sartoshi for the mfer in all.

Birth  
at dawn’s first light,  
an mfer takes flight,  
to learn the wrongs,  
that found the rights.  
~goldenfleye
